approach: Mathematical modeling using Computer Vision (CV-ML) ensemble approach with handcrafted features. This model extracts traditional image features (texture with GLCM and LBP, shape with HOG and edge detection, statistical moments, and frequency analysis with Fourier transform) from lung CT scans and combines multiple machine learning models (Random Forest, SVM, and KNN) in a voting ensemble.
